// Phase 22: notebook, research template, reproducible env fingerprint.
samūhalakṣaṇaḥ citra-saṃkhyāḥ eka dve trīṇi catvāri pañca.
āhvānam std.data.describe citra-saṃkhyāḥ phalaṃ nidadhāti.
kośaḥ sandarbhaḥ.
sthāpanam sandarbhaḥ metric saṃkhyā 0.9 iti.
āhvānam std.research.template_render vākyam metric={{metric}} iti sandarbhaḥ phalaṃ nidadhāti.
kośaḥ parisaraḥ.
sthāpanam parisaraḥ seed vākyam sapta iti.
āhvānam std.env.fingerprint parisaraḥ phalaṃ nidadhāti.
gaṇakaḥ phalaṃ darśayati.
